<br>
You want to do your epic?  Start learning how to raid.  <br>
Ready to learn how to raid?  Start doing Training raids.<br>
How are Training raids?  Read on...<br>
<br>
Training Raids are to help prepare you for the major mobs.  If you in a group tend to die regularly then you need to do this.<br>
<br>
Facts:<br>
On a raid if you do not understand what your role is you will die<br>
<br>
On a raid if you do not understand what your role is another person will die<br>
<br>
On a raid if you do not understand what your role is the entire raiding party can die.<br>
<br>
Do not attend a training raid looking for exp<br>
<br>
Do not attend a training raid looking for loot<br>
<br>
Do not attend a training raid watching TV<br>
<br>
Do not attend a training raid while reading a book.<br>
<br>
Do not show up late to a training raid<br>
<br>
Do not be discourteous to the ones who are there.<br>
<br>
You will gain invaluable insight on how to perform<br>
<br>
You will gain experiance on how a higher raid is done<br>
<br>
You will be better prepared to know how to handle higher mobs <br>
<br>
<br>
Now who wants to go on a training raid? <p>Reinu <BR>
